            </div>
            <div class="notice-item">
              <div class="ni-dot new"></div>
              <div class="ni-info">
                <div class="ni-title">4월 강좌 수강 신청 시작 안내</div>
                <div class="ni-time">어제 17:00</div>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="notice-item">
              <div class="ni-dot new"></div>
              <div class="ni-info">
                <div class="ni-title">봄 학기 특별 할인 이벤트 승인</div>
                <div class="ni-time">2026-03-30</div>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="notice-item">
              <div class="ni-dot read"></div>
              <div class="ni-info">
                <div class="ni-title">신규 강사 채용 공고 게시 완료</div>
                <div class="ni-time">2026-03-29</div>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="notice-item">
              <div class="ni-dot read"></div>
              <div class="ni-info">
                <div class="ni-title">3월 재무 보고서 제출 완료</div>
                <div class="ni-time">2026-03-28</div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Schedule -->
      <div class="panel">
        <div class="panel-head">
          <div class="panel-title"><div class="pt-dot" style="background:#ffd700"></div>오늘 일정</div>
          <a class="panel-more" href="#">주간 보기 →</a>
        </div>
        <div class="panel-body">
          <div class="sched-list">
            <div class="sched-item">
              <div class="sched-time">09:00</div>
              <div class="sched-body">
                <div class="sched-title">월간 운영 회의</div>
                <div class="sched-loc">2층 회의실 · 전 강사</div>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="sched-item">
              <div class="sched-time">10:30</div>
              <div class="sched-body s2">
                <div class="sched-title">하타요가 초급반</div>
                <div class="sched-loc">A홀 · 김지영 강사</div>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="sched-item">
              <div class="sched-time">13:00</div>
              <div class="sched-body s3">
                <div class="sched-title">시설 점검 미팅</div>
                <div class="sched-loc">1층 로비 · 총무팀</div>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="sched-item">
              <div class="sched-time">15:00</div>
              <div class="sched-body s4">
                <div class="sched-title">신규 강사 면접</div>
                <div class="sched-loc">3층 면접실 · 인사팀</div>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="sched-item">
              <div class="sched-time">18:30</div>
              <div class="sched-body">
                <div class="sched-title">저녁 명상 클래스</div>
                <div class="sched-loc">B홀 · 최현우 강사</div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Team Photos -->
      <div class="panel">
        <div class="panel-head">
          <div class="panel-title"><div class="pt-dot" style="background:#52b788"></div>강사진</div>
          <a class="panel-more" href="#">전체 프로필 →</a>
        </div>
        <div class="panel-body">
          <div class="team-grid">
            <div class="team-card">
              <img src="<%= imgs[4] %>" alt="강사1">
              <div class="team-card-info">
                <div class="team-card-name">김지영</div>
                <div class="team-card-role">하타요가</div>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="team-card">
              <img src="<%= imgs[5] %>" alt="강사2">
              <div class="team-card-info">
                <div class="team-card-name">최현우</div>
                <div class="team-card-role">명상·호흡</div>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="team-card">
              <img src="<%= imgs[0] %>" alt="강사3">
              <div class="team-card-info">
                <div class="team-card-name">박소연</div>
                <div class="team-card-role">필라테스</div>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="team-card">
              <img src="<%= imgs[1] %>" alt="강사4">
              <div class="team-card-info">
                <div class="team-card-name">이준혁</div>
                <div class="team-card-role">아쉬탕가</div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

    </div>

    <!-- WIDE BANNER (uses img 2) -->
    <div class="wide-banner">
      <img src="<%= imgs[2] %>" alt="프로그램 배너">
      <div class="wb-overlay">
        <div class="wb-text">
          <h3>여름 집중 프로그램 사전 예약 시작</h3>
          <p>7월 ~ 8월 · 숙박형 리트릿 포함 · 정원 30명 한정</p>
        </div>
        <button class="wb-cta">지금 예약하기</button>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- METRICS ROW -->
    <div class="metrics-grid">
      <div class="metric-card">
        <div class="metric-icon">🧘</div>
        <div class="metric-info">
          <div class="metric-label">총 누적 수강생</div>
          <div class="metric-val">8,540</div>
          <div class="metric-sub">개원 이래 누계</div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="metric-card">
        <div class="metric-icon">⭐</div>
        <div class="metric-info">
          <div class="metric-label">강좌 평균 만족도</div>
          <div class="metric-val">4.87</div>
          <div class="metric-sub">/ 5점 만점 · 최근 3개월</div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="metric-card">
        <div class="metric-icon">📅</div>
        <div class="metric-info">
          <div class="metric-label">이번 주 예약 건수</div>
          <div class="metric-val">312</div>
          <div class="metric-sub">전주 대비 +18%</div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

  </main>
</div>

<!-- FOOTER -->
<footer>
  <div class="ft-brand">
    <div class="ft-logo">
      <div class="ft-logo-mark">L</div>
      <span class="ft-logo-name">루카스 아트센터</span>
    </div>
    <p>몸과 마음의 균형을 찾는 공간.<br>
       전문 강사진과 체계적인 프로그램으로<br>
       건강한 일상을 만들어 드립니다.</p>
  </div>
  <div class="ft-col">
    <h4>바로가기</h4>
    <ul>
      <li><a href="#">강좌 안내</a></li>
      <li><a href="#">강사 소개</a></li>
      <li><a href="#">공간 예약</a></li>
      <li><a href="#">이벤트</a></li>
    </ul>
  </div>
  <div class="ft-col">
    <h4>고객 지원</h4>
    <ul>
      <li><a href="#">공지사항</a></li>
      <li><a href="#">자주 묻는 질문</a></li>
      <li><a href="#">1:1 문의</a></li>
      <li><a href="#">오시는 길</a></li>
    </ul>
  </div>
</footer>
<div class="ft-bottom">
  <span>© 2026 루카스 아트센터. All rights reserved.</span>
  <span>시안 테마 <a href="#">#<%= themeId %></a> · 레이아웃 <%= layoutId %></span>
</div>

<!-- SIANN BADGE -->
<div class="siann-badge">
  <div class="siann-badge-title">시안 선택 — L10</div>
  <div class="siann-badge-grid">
    <% for(let i = 1; i <= 20; i++) { %>
      <a href="/siann-10/<%= i %>" class="<%= i === themeId ? 'cur' : '' %>"><%= i %></a>
    <% } %>
  </div>
</div>

</body>
</html>
